
            Video
            Can you spot a laboratory-made diamond?
            If you're lucky enough to give or receive a piece of diamond jewellery - do you think you'd know what you're looking at? There's a debate raging about whether diamonds created in a laboratory will start to threaten the popularity of natural, mined diamonds. The BBC's Sharanjit Leyl paid a visit to the world's largest firm making lab grown diamonds in Singapore.
                
                        21 Oct 2015
                    
                
        
